title: Maid of Honor
description:
It was supposed to be the happiest day of Jen's life, but there was only one problem- her maid of honor.

Written by Ariel Karlin

Featuring Chrissy Shackelford, Tessa Hersh, Maya Deshmukh, Willy Appelman and Michael Delisle
Directed by Matt Gehring
Shot by Thursday Shoots
Edited by Phillip Russell
